mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲錢係自己嘅<br />\n如果拍拖就話「一齊儲」<br />\ntouch wood真係分手<br />\n咁筆錢點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到啱時間結婚左右<br />\n「結婚錢」咪先同另外一半夾<br />\n如果到呢一刻佢話佢一直都無儲錢<br />\n其實你都好應該考慮下其實佢啱唔啱同你結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c627763e8ce1aca30d18b1504e16394d63d67d89","tid":1988752,"uid":240336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82ce08e3d5e01e71fff9caf26b4755c1d845d007","tid":1988752,"uid":356579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad47357eb71906b9be836c9ac8ab90e4b6ac4896","tid":1988752,"uid":240336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad79d20b3cccc1e8d56c6dcc7781576c97918458","tid":1988752,"uid":356579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T15:21:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T16:12:05.000Z","msg":"好難講，乜男人都有，冇可能一概而論<br />\n但我記得你，太多擔心，搞到自己唔開心，段關係點會健康？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T16:20:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T03:19:49.000Z","msg":"你嘅擔心來自沒有信心，是對自己還是對佢沒有信心？ 這都可以是跟成長經歷有關，冇話對與錯的。<br />\n我結左幾年婚，可以同你講，唔好諗住結婚就係終結，你仍然都要注入新的滿足感俾你老公而唔係食之前積落的感情老本。而滿足感的產生方法好睇個人，你作為佢最親近嘅人應該最清楚，佢要安定，你俾到安定感佢就可以，唔駛諗咁多。"}]}